2014-09-30  Yuva  <yuva@codemancers.com>

	* Add a timer to ZmqCommandSocket. This is a one shot timer, which will
	be used before sending the command. If socket fails to receive any
	response, then command sending is marked as failed, and context and
	socket are reset.

	* Use QSharedPointer<> for pointers in zmqsockets

